<bioghist encodinganalog="545"><head>History of Xavier University Department of Nursing</head><p>The Xavier University Department of Nursing came to the Xavier campus after the purchase of Edgecliff College from the Sisters of Mercy  in 1983 and the subsequent sale of the Edgecliff campus in 1987. Originally in Xavier's College of Professional Studies this Department now resides in Xavier's College of Social Sciences, Health &amp; Education.</p><bioghist><p></p></bioghist></bioghist><scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a"><head>Scope and Content</head><p>The materials in this collection consist chiefly in departmental minutes, correspondence, reports, self-studies, and proposals.</p><scopecontent><p></p></scopecontent></scopecontent><arrangement encodinganalog="351$b"><head>Statement of Arrangement</head><p>Materials in this collection are arranged by general series:</p><list type="simple"><item>Minutes, Correspondence, and Reports</item><item>Brochures</item><item>Studies and Proposals</item><item>Recent Program Developments</item></list></arrangement><relatedmaterial encodinganalog="544 1"><head>Related Material</head><p>See also XUA-37, Edgecliff College records for limited additional information about the Nursing Department while at Edgecliff College.</p></relatedmaterial><accessrestrict encodinganalog="506"><head>Restrictions on Access</head><p>Some materials may have restricted access. Please contact the archives staff.</p></accessrestrict><prefercite encodinganalog="524"><head>Preferred Citation</head><p>Box Number, Folder Number, XUA-74, Xavier University Department of Nursing records, Special Collections and University Archives, Xavier University Library, Cincinnati, Ohio.</p></prefercite><accruals encodinganalog="584"><head>Accruals</head><p>Additions to this collection are expected.</p></accruals><controlaccess><head>Indexing Terms</head><p>The following terms have been used to index the description of this collection in the library's online public access ca